@startuml name Node DevOps Demo Deployment Flow
top to bottom direction

actor Developer
actor User

rectangle "GitHub Repository" as repo
rectangle "GitHub Actions" as gha
rectangle "Docker Hub" as hub

node "AWS EC2 Instance" {
  rectangle "Docker Compose" {
    rectangle "Node.js App Container" as app
    database "PostgreSQL Container" as postgres
  }
}

Developer --> repo : push changes
repo --> gha : trigger workflow
gha --> hub : build and push image
gha --> app : deploy latest image via SSH
User --> app : access application
app --> postgres : read/write data
@enduml